 315:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c ****             * This may cause some confusion in some cases - for example, if
 316:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c ****             * configMAX_SYSCALL_INTERRUPT_PRIORITY is set to 5, both 5 and 4
