 322:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c ****             * to 4, this confusion does not happen and the behaviour remains the same.
 323:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c ****             *
 324:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/portable/GCC/ARM_CM3/port.c ****             * The following assert ensures that the sub-priority bit in the
